Title: Requires certain health insurance policies to provide coverage for diabetes screening for people having a body mass index of 23 or greater
Summary: Requires certain health insurance policies to provide coverage for diabetes screening for people having a body mass index of 23 or greater.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, in relation to requiring certain health insurance policies to provide coverage for diabetes screening for people having a body mass index of 23 or greater
